quran[10]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,9,"Odoma (nabiyyicha) maleykaa isa gooneeyyuu dhugumatti silaa (nama) dhiira isa taasifneeti waan isaan walitti fakkeessan isaan irratti wal fakkeesina turre.",""
  6,10,"Dhugumatti, ergamoota si dura turanitti qoosamee ture. Isaan irraa warra qoosanitti wanti isaan itti qoosaa turan isaanitti marse.",""
  6,11,"Jedhi: ""dachii keessa deemaa; ergasii booddeen warra dhugaa kijibsiisee akkam akka ta’e ilaalaa.""",""
  6,12,"Ini: \"w i t ilan wayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan\"? Ini: \"d Öebbi\". Iura, deg iman iS, aêunu. A kwen Issemlil i wass n tnekra, ur ccekk fellas. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ur ppamnen.""Wantoonni samiileefi dachii keessa jiran hundi kan eenyuuti?"Ini: \"w i t ilan wayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan\"? Ini: \"d Öebbi\". Iura, deg iman iS, aêunu. A kwen Issemlil i wass n tnekra, ur ccekk fellas. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ur ppamnen." jedhi. “Kan Rabbiiti” jedhi. Lubbuu Isaa irratti rahmata barreessee jira. Dhugumatti, Guyyaa Qiyaamaa mamiin isa keessa hin jirreef walitti isin qaba. Isaan lubbuulee isaanii hoongessan, isaan hin amananu.","Ini: \"w i t ilan wayen akw illan di tmurt akked igenwan\"? Ini: \"d Öebbi\". Iura, deg iman iS, aêunu. A kwen Issemlil i wass n tnekra, ur ccekk fellas. Wid isxesôen iman nnsen, ur ppamnen."
  6,13,"Wanti halkaniifi guyyaa keessa callises kan isaati. Inni dhagayaa, beekaadha.",""
  6,14,"Jedhi ""Sila Rabbiin malee gabbaramaa biraa godhadhaa? (inni) uumaa samiifi dachiiti, inni ni nyaachisa hin nyaatu"". jedhi ""Ani jalqaba nama Rabbiif bulee ta'uuttin ajajame. Mushrikoota irraas hin ta'in (naan jedhame)"".",""
  6,15,"Ini: \"nek ugade$, ma aâûa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan\".""Ani yoon Gooftaa kiyyatti dilaaye adabbii guyyaa guddaan sodaadha"Ini: \"nek ugade$, ma aâûa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan\"." jedhi.","Ini: \"nek ugade$, ma aâûa$ Mass iw, aâaqeb n wass ameqwôaêan\"."
  6,16,"Namni guyyaa san isa (adabicha) irraa deebifame, dhugumatti (Rabbiin) isa mararfateera. Kun milkii guddaadha.",""
  6,17,"Yoo Rabbiin miidhaan si tuqe, Isa malee deemsisaan isaaf hin jiru. Yoo toltuudhaan si tuqe, Inni waan hunda irratti danda’aadha.",""
  6,18,"Inni gabroota Isaa irratti mo’ataadha. Inni ogeessa, keessa beekaadha.",""
